snippet.title: Physics Drop New Multiplayer Mode
snippet.description:
NEW MULTIPLAYER GAME MODE 
Beat friends & other players! Each match has 3 random levels. To win a match, complete at least 2 before your opponent. Options:
- QUICK MATCH. Play against a random player. A play room will be created as soon as there is one available.
- INVITE FRIENDS. Available players will appear for you to pick one. Invite friends and challenge them! 
- INVITATIONS. Click to accept an invitation and to allow players nearby to find you.
Try now and download from Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dreamed.physicsdrop
an App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/physics-drop/id1202944857?mt=8&ign-mpt=uo%3D4
